	<description>The eHealthConnector (eHC) is a convenience API for IHE transactions and CDA-CH documents. It supports functionalities for cross-enterprise sharing of documents and master patient index (MPI) connection using IHE transactions and also supports CDA-CH content profiles.It allows easy access and conformity to the Swiss eHealth trust space.
The eHC is built on the basis of the MDHT HITSP runtime libraries and the OHT IHE profiles.</description>

